title: Vox Machina Ep. 10 - K'Varn Revealed
description: The team jumps right in to a fight with some undead, followed by a dangerous encounter in the water. Their bad luck only continues when a scrying spell reveals the identity of the mysterious 'K'varn', and a city deep underground...
